main.success.invite.embeds.0.title: Thanks for inviting MC Linker!
main.success.invite.embeds.0.description:
To get started, please connect your Minecraft server to the bot:

‚Ä¢ Install the **Discord-Linker** plugin from [SpigotMC](https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/discord-linker.98749/), [Modrinth](https://modrinth.com/plugin/discord-linker) or from the [Aternos Plugin List](https://aternos.org/addons/a/spigot/98749) to your Minecraft server.
‚Ä¢ Execute </connect plugin:932257443394777129> in Discord.
‚Ä¢ Execute the command from the embed in Minecraft.

**That's it!**
You can now create a chat-bridge using </chatchannel add:932257443394777128> or check out any of the other commands!

If you need more help, join the [Support Server](https://discord.gg/rX36kZUGNK) or visit the [MC Linker Guide](https://guide.mclinker.com).
